https://youtu.be/jF-alcdebcc
</div></figure>
<!-- /wp:embed -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>As a part of the Kentuckiana community, we want our doors to be open to everyone and be a support for the entire LGBTQIA+ population. It’s about striking the balance of giving kids the opportunity to be themselves, but also teaching them how to take responsibility and give back.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

